com.coasttocoastresearch.apg

Packages that use com.coasttocoastresearch.apg
com.coasttocoastresearch.apg Provides classes for the ABNF parser generator, the generated parsers and all necessary supporting classes.

Classes in com.coasttocoastresearch.apg used by com.coasttocoastresearch.apg
Ast
          A class representation of the parser-generated Abstract Syntax Tree (AST).
Ast.AstCallback
          The base class for all AST callback functions.
Ast.CallbackData
          The parser provisions each callback function with an instance of this class.
GeneratorGrammar.RuleNames
          This enum provides easy to remember enum constants for locating the rule identifiers and names.
GeneratorGrammar.UdtNames
          This enum provides easy to remember enum constants for locating the rule identifiers and names.
Grammar
          The Grammar class is the interface between the Parser and the Parser Generator.
Parser
          Parsers are built by initializing this class with a Generator-generated Grammar and optional user-defined terminals and rule callback functions.
Parser.CallbackData
          Provisioned by the Parser for user-defined rule and UDT callback functions.
Parser.Result
          Defines the Parser's results.
Parser.RuleCallback
          The base class for all user-defined rule callback functions.
Parser.UdtCallback
          Base class for all User Defined Terminals (UDT).
Statistics
          The Statistics class is used to collect and display the statistics on which nodes were visited (hit) by the parser in its journey through the syntax tree and the result of each hit - that is, whether the node matched a phrase of the input string or not.
Trace
          The Trace class will generate a detailed information record for every operator node the Parser visits during its journey through the syntax tree.
UdtLib.Comment
           
UdtLib.LineEnd
           
UdtLib.QuotedString
           
Utilities.LineCatalog.Line
          Class defining a catalog record for an individual line of text.
